bsp;in khá rõ nét, giúp màu mực bền lâu tiện cho việc lưu trữ.</span></p><div id=\"attachment_1510\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" style=\"margin: 5px 20px 20px 0px; padding: 5px 3px 10px; line-height: 1.5; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 1px solid rgb(240, 240, 240); max-width: 96%; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; width: 1514px;\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1510\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1510\" src=\"https://vanphongpham247.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Gi%E1%BA%A5y-in-Double-A-A5-%C4%90L70-gsm-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1504\" height=\"1996\" srcset=\"https://vanphongpham247.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Giấy-in-Double-A-A5-ĐL70-gsm-1.jpg 1504w, https://vanphongpham247.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Giấy-in-Double-A-A5-ĐL70-gsm-1-226x300.jpg 226w, https://vanphongpham247.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Giấy-in-Double-A-A5-ĐL70-gsm-1-768x1019.jpg 768w, https://vanphongpham247.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Giấy-in-Double-A-A5-ĐL70-gsm-1-772x1024.jpg 772w, https://vanphongpham247.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Giấy-in-Double-A-A5-ĐL70-gsm-1-600x796.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1504px) 100vw, 1504px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; border-style: none; max-width: 98.5%; height: auto; width: auto;\"><p id=\"caption-attachment-1510\" class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 4px 5px; line-height: 17px; font-size: 11px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px;\">Giấy in Double A A5 ĐL70 gsm</span></p></div><p style=\"padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px;\">Sản phẩm có&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 700;\"><a href=\"https://vanphongpham247.vn/san-pham/giay-a4-double-a-70-90/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(87, 84, 84); cursor: pointer;\">Giấy in Double A A4</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://vanphongpham247.vn/san-pham/giay-double-a-a3-dl-70gsm/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(87, 84, 84); cursor: pointer;\">Giấy in Double A A3</a></span></span></p>', 14, 16, '2021-07-13 15:17:47', '2021-07-13 15:17:47');
